TY  - JOUR
T1  - The Industrial Organization of Congress; or, Why Legislatures, Like Firms, Are Not Organized as Markets
AU  - Weingast, Barry R.
AU  - Marshall, William J.
Y1  - 1988/02/01
PY  - 1988
DA  - 1988/02/01
N1  - doi: 10.1086/261528
